### 2.4 Icon Sizing System
- Define icon sizes in CSS variables: `--icon-{size}`
- Standard sizes: xs(16px), sm(20px), md(24px), lg(32px), xl(40px)
- Use consistent stroke width for outline icons
- Proper spacing around icons in text

## 3. Error Boundaries & Empty States

### 3.1 Error Boundaries
- All major sections must have error boundaries
- Consistent error message styling
- Provide recovery options when possible
- Log errors for debugging
- User-friendly error messages (no technical jargon)

### 3.2 Empty States
- Every list/table must have empty state design
- Provide clear guidance on what to do next
- Use illustrations or icons for visual appeal
- Include CTAs when appropriate
- Maintain brand voice in empty state copy

### 3.3 Loading States
- Skeleton screens for content loading
- Use the app **Spinner** component (`@/components/ui/Spinner`) for all loading indicators (buttons, tables, pages).
- Progress indicators for multi-step processes
- Avoid blocking entire UI when possible

### 3.4 Error/Empty Component Structure
```
